 1:  HTML5 contenteditable attribute not working properly on iOS7 Mobile Safariï¼š
     Answer:
        * {
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
        }

        input,
        textarea,
        [contenteditable] {
            -webkit-user-select: text;
            user-select: text;
        }
